{
    "body": "<p>Despite their penchant for brutal competitions, sahuagin are communal creatures that live and hunt in groups for their mutual good; these groups range from small raiding parties to massive underwater cities. Here are some example encounters using the various types of sahuagin presented in this section.</p>", 
    "name": "Encounters", 
